{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-04",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_04_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 4 - The Black Bird",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 2,
  "page_total": 7,
  "page_start_sec": 253.74,
  "page_end_sec": 501.4,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.737,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 253.74,
      "end": 254.12,
      "text": "Oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 254.24,
      "end": 255.1,
      "text": "please don't,"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.62,
      "end": 256.24,
      "text": "she whispered."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.184,
      "end": 258.02,
      "text": "Spade shrugged again.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 259.232,
      "end": 260.02,
      "text": "That's the way it was.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 260.63,
      "end": 262.88,
      "text": "He glanced at the watch on his wrist and"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.88,
      "end": 265.14,
      "text": "moved from his chair to the settee beside her."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.464,
      "end": 268.24,
      "text": "There's no time for worrying about that now.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 268.88,
      "end": 270.7,
      "text": "His voice was amiable but firm."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.416,
      "end": 272.88,
      "text": "Out there,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 272.92,
      "end": 276.4,
      "text": "a flock of policemen and reporters and assistant district attorneys"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.62,
      "end": 278.68,
      "text": "are running around with their noses to the ground."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.53,
      "end": 280.64,
      "text": "What do you want to do?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 281.55,
      "end": 283.22,
      "text": "I want you to save me",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 284.3,
      "end": 285.06,
      "text": "from—from all of it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 285.26,
      "end": 286.84,
      "text": "she said in a thin,"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.96,
      "end": 287.82,
      "text": "tremulous voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.98,
      "end": 290.78,
      "text": "She put her hand timidly on his forearm.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 291.8,
      "end": 292.24,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 292.38,
      "end": 292.7,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.32,
      "end": 294.26,
      "text": "do they know about me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.36,
      "end": 295.72,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 296.6,
      "end": 297.9,
      "text": "I wanted to see you first.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 298.92,
      "end": 299.4,
      "text": "What?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 300.18,
      "end": 302.84,
      "text": "What would they think if they knew about the way I came to you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 302.98,
      "end": 303.92,
      "text": "with those lies?"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.728,
      "end": 308.22,
      "text": "That wouldn't mean anything to the police except guilt.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 309.344,
      "end": 311.42,
      "text": "That's why I've been stalling them till I could see you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 312.56,
      "end": 312.88,
      "text": "I thought",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 312.96,
      "end": 315.1,
      "text": "maybe we wouldn't have to let them know at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.04,
      "end": 316.74,
      "text": "We ought to be able",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 316.74,
      "end": 319.65,
      "text": "to fake a story that will rock them to sleep if necessary.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 321.1,
      "end": 321.34,
      "text": "\"'Mr.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 321.52,
      "end": 321.84,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.11,
      "end": 325.36,
      "text": "you don't think I had anything to do with—the murders,"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.56,
      "end": 326.04,
      "text": "do you?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.06,
      "end": 328.44,
      "text": "He grinned at her and said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 329.54,
      "end": 330.82,
      "text": "\"'I forgot to ask you that.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 331.04,
      "end": 331.98,
      "text": "Did you?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.4,
      "end": 333.24,
      "text": "\"'No.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 333.952,
      "end": 334.34,
      "text": "\"'That's good."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.16,
      "end": 336.75,
      "text": "Now what are we going to tell the police?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 338.26,
      "end": 340.42,
      "text": "She squirmed on her end of the settee and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 340.42,
      "end": 342.22,
      "text": "her eyes wavered between heavy lashes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.76,
      "end": 345.9,
      "text": "as if trying and failing to free their gaze from his."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.02,
      "end": 349.04,
      "text": "She seemed smaller and very young and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 349.14,
      "end": 349.42,
      "text": "oppressed."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.232,
      "end": 353.62,
      "text": "\"'Must they know about me at all?' she asked.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 354.12,
      "end": 355.98,
      "text": "\"'I think I'd rather die than that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.08,
      "end": 356.24,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.34,
      "end": 356.64,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.16,
      "end": 358.96,
      "text": "I can't explain now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.14,
      "end": 360.9,
      "text": "but can't you somehow manage"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.9,
      "end": 362.88,
      "text": "so that you can shield me from them altogether,"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.2,
      "end": 365.08,
      "text": "so I won't have to answer their questions?"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.5,
      "end": 367.68,
      "text": "I couldn't stand being questioned,"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.8,
      "end": 367.96,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 368.02,
      "end": 368.32,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 368.52,
      "end": 369.98,
      "text": "I would rather die."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.28,
      "end": 371.552,
      "text": "Can't you?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 372.54,
      "end": 373.7,
      "text": "\"'Maybe,' he said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 374.5,
      "end": 376.51,
      "text": "But I'll have to know what it's all about.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 377.88,
      "end": 379.82,
      "text": "She went down on her knees at his knees.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 380.64,
      "end": 382.06,
      "text": "She held her face up to him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 382.3,
      "end": 383.64,
      "text": "Her face was wan,"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.1,
      "end": 384.44,
      "text": "taut,"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.46,
      "end": 386.62,
      "text": "and fearful over taut clasped hands."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.52,
      "end": 390.74,
      "text": "\"'I haven't lived a good life,' she cried.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 391.88,
      "end": 392.22,
      "text": "I'm bad,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 392.56,
      "end": 393.86,
      "text": "worse than you could know,"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.08,
      "end": 395.74,
      "text": "but I'm not all bad."
    },
    {
      "start": 396.39,
      "end": 397.16,
      "text": "Look at me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.2,
      "end": 397.38,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.44,
      "end": 397.78,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 398.46,
      "end": 399.28,
      "text": "You know I'm not"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.28,
      "end": 399.84,
      "text": "all bad,"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.92,
      "end": 400.4,
      "text": "don't you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 400.52,
      "end": 401.84,
      "text": "You can see that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.92,
      "end": 402.34,
      "text": "can't you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.24,
      "end": 404.78,
      "text": "Then can't you trust me a little?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 405.88,
      "end": 406.52,
      "text": "I'm so alone",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 406.68,
      "end": 407.16,
      "text": "and afraid,"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.42,
      "end": 410.32,
      "text": "and I've got nobody to help me if you won't help me."
    },
    {
      "start": 410.83,
      "end": 412.88,
      "text": "I know I've no right to ask"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.88,
      "end": 414.76,
      "text": "you to trust me if I won't trust you."
    },
    {
      "start": 415.56,
      "end": 416.56,
      "text": "I do trust you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 416.7,
      "end": 418.54,
      "text": "but I can't tell you."
    },
    {
      "start": 418.85,
      "end": 420.36,
      "text": "I can't tell you now."
    },
    {
      "start": 421.376,
      "end": 422.08,
      "text": "Later I will,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 422.26,
      "end": 423.08,
      "text": "when I can."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.32,
      "end": 424.7,
      "text": "I'm afraid,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 424.86,
      "end": 425.02,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 425.12,
      "end": 425.42,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 425.6,
      "end": 427.42,
      "text": "I'm afraid of trusting you."
    },
    {
      "start": 427.61,
      "end": 428.82,
      "text": "I don't mean that."
    },
    {
      "start": 429.3,
      "end": 430.26,
      "text": "I do trust you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.32,
      "end": 432.54,
      "text": "but—but I trusted Floyd,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 432.8,
      "end": 436.14,
      "text": "and I've nobody else—nobody else,"
    },
    {
      "start": 436.2,
      "end": 436.44,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.5,
      "end": 436.86,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 438.12,
      "end": 439.08,
      "text": "You can save me.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 439.4,
      "end": 441.1,
      "text": "You've said you can save me."
    },
    {
      "start": 441.88,
      "end": 443.6,
      "text": "If I hadn't believed you can save me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 443.86,
      "end": 446.66,
      "text": "I would have run away today instead of sending for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 446.8,
      "end": 449.5,
      "text": "If I thought anybody else could save me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.68,
      "end": 451.5,
      "text": "would I be down on my knees to you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.03,
      "end": 454.02,
      "text": "I know this isn't fair of me."
    },
    {
      "start": 454.8,
      "end": 455.52,
      "text": "But be generous,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 455.7,
      "end": 455.88,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 455.96,
      "end": 456.26,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.992,
      "end": 458.28,
      "text": "Don't ask me to be fair."
    },
    {
      "start": 458.52,
      "end": 459.68,
      "text": "You're strong."
    },
    {
      "start": 459.92,
      "end": 461.04,
      "text": "You're resourceful."
    },
    {
      "start": 461.08,
      "end": 461.88,
      "text": "You're brave."
    },
    {
      "start": 462.73,
      "end": 464.24,
      "text": "You can spare me some",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 464.24,
      "end": 466.34,
      "text": "of that strength and resourcefulness and courage,"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.42,
      "end": 466.8,
      "text": "surely."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.36,
      "end": 468.3,
      "text": "Help me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.34,
      "end": 468.48,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.6,
      "end": 468.92,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.06,
      "end": 469.86,
      "text": "Help me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.9,
      "end": 470.48,
      "text": "because I"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.54,
      "end": 471.56,
      "text": "need help so badly."
    },
    {
      "start": 471.86,
      "end": 473.74,
      "text": "Because if you don't,"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.74,
      "end": 475.4,
      "text": "where will I find anyone who can,"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.68,
      "end": 476.38,
      "text": "however willing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 477.68,
      "end": 478.04,
      "text": "\"'Help me?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 478.72,
      "end": 481.24,
      "text": "I've no right to ask you to help me blindly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.46,
      "end": 482.94,
      "text": "but I do ask you."
    },
    {
      "start": 483.1,
      "end": 484.34,
      "text": "Be generous,"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.54,
      "end": 484.74,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.8,
      "end": 485.14,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.34,
      "end": 486.82,
      "text": "You can save me."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.0,
      "end": 487.68,
      "text": "You can."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.94,
      "end": 489.344,
      "text": "Won't you?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.41,
      "end": 491.06,
      "text": "Spade,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 491.16,
      "end": 493.56,
      "text": "who had held his breath throughout much of this speech,"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.82,
      "end": 496.0,
      "text": "now emptied his lungs with a long"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.12,
      "end": 498.78,
      "text": "sighing exhalation between pursed lips and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.84,
      "end": 501.4,
      "text": "\"'You won't need much of anybody's help.",
      "para_break": true
    }
  ]
}